data.description: Welcome Home! This 1728 sqft 4/2 Ranch sits on 1.66 acres and offers a bonus 24 x 60 separate In-Law suite/work shop.  As you enter you will see Family room with a corner fireplace.  Granite counters in gourmet kitchen with island, built-ins and plenty of custom cabinets. Large master w/ walk in closet and large tiled bath is on the left side of the family room and other bedrooms are on the right and rear.  New Lux vinyl flooring throughout the home, (no carpet) Covered front porch & back screened in patio with fenced in front and back yard.  Rear building that houses a true in-law suite has bedroom, bathroom, mini kitchen... that's heated and cooled with its own Septic system and Workshop with a garage bay along with Separate power & water as well as a detached 16x24 metal carport.  The rear building has its own private entrance and its owns self contained fencing.  This immaculate home is move-in ready and priced to sell!  NO HOA Veterans may qualify to assume the current VA loan that's in place.  Please reach out to David Wilkes KW at (678-438-8118 for further.
